<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10145364>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5–8. Triplocania oiapoque n. sp. (Holotype male). 5. Phallosome. 6–7. Hypandrium. 8. Clunium, epiproct and left paraproct. Scales in mm." ;
